These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, artichoke
City: paris, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Food         | artichoke | broccoli |
| City     | paris | colone    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, fanta
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage          | water     | fanta |
| Birthday   | december | march  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, turkish
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | turkish     | brazilian |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Sport   | surfing         | soccer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
