.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, pop
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
House: townhouse, ranch-style
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Music-Genre           | soul | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | scientific      |
| House           | townhouse      | ranch-style          |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton       |

