House: cape-cod, palace
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, techno
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the palace house is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| House         | palace        | cape-cod |
| Music-Genre         | blues          | techno     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 